13	2022-10-05	\N	Call Out	* Living in ATL, moving to Austin, gave EM in $4k\r\n* Paid $37k for upgrades. We got pregnant, job change, and increased interest rates.\r\n* We want to break our contract without losing all of the money.\r\n* The home is being built. A new home in a development.\r\n* Property was $750k\r\n* We were sure about the exterior, but the brick was not available, but the seller could not provide exact same brick – gave no option that this was the only way ahead\r\n* Text – we do not want to compromise on the look\r\n* Assistant Vice President\r\n* From my eyes, there is not much room they have left for us\r\n* **Client will email whether he wants to move forward with a consultation**	20	3
